        "Guillaume Cartier"
        (<p>)
        (<division> title: "Announcement"
        (<cite>
          "Date: Thursday, November 27, 2008" (<br>)
          "Time: 7:00pm - 9:00pm" (<br>)
          "Location: Room 3195, André-Aisenstadt Building, Université de Montréal" (<br>)
